    <briefdescription>
<para>Union-find data structure for representing disjoin sets of elements with few very quick operations: 1) union of two sets in one, 2) checking whether two elements pertain to the same set, 3) finding representative element (root) of each set by any set&apos;s element. </para>
    </briefdescription>
